div.p:
The Priſoner had little to ſay in his Defence;
he endeavour'd to prove himſelf Alibi;
ſo that the Trial turn'd upon this ſingle Queſtion,
whether the ſaid Timothy Trim and
Jack, were the ſame Perſon? which was
prov'd by ſuch plain Tokens, and particularly
by a Mole under the left Pap, that


there was no withſtanding the Evidence;
therefore the Worſhipful Mr. Juſtice committed
him, in order to his Tryal.

sp.p:
Thou haſt ſo many If's and And's;
prithee diſpatch; it might have been over before
this time.

